"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&End;</keycombo> </shortcut> "
"<guimenu>Jogo</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Terminar o Jogo</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:257
#, no-c-format
msgid "Ends a running game."
